data.description: EXPERIENCE THE ULTIMATE COMBINATION OF NATURE AND LUXURY LIVING AT ITS FINEST! Welcome to Chapin Woods Place, this property boasts extensive acreage complemented by an exquisitely designed home. As you enter, the grand staircase welcomes you, leading to the expansive living room adorned with a warm and inviting fireplace to enjoy on those cold winter evenings. Prepare to be amazed by the gourmet kitchen, featuring high end, commercial grade Forno appliances including 8 burner double oven gas stove, a 60" double door refrigerator/freezer combo, angel stone countertops and backsplash, a butler pantry with a glass-front wine cooler and mini fridge, soft-closing doors and drawers, and a deep pantry.  The flexible space on the main level allows you to unleash your creativity and transform it into an office, library, or a peaceful nook. With a choice between a main floor suite or a spacious upstairs primary suite, this residence offers six bedrooms and 4.5 baths to accommodate your every need. The upstairs suite comes complete with a sitting room, tray ceiling, two walk-in closets, a deluxe bathroom featuring a bidet upgraded toilet, walk-in shower, and a separate soak tub.  Laundry will never be a hassle with two laundry rooms, one on the main level and another on the upstairs level. The main laundry room is equipped with a LG smart washer and dryer, while a combo washer/dryer is conveniently located on the main level. The unfinished basement presents an exciting opportunity for you to customize the space according to your preferences. Additionally, the basement houses the Aquasauna whole house water filter with UV light and a tankless hot water heater, providing ultimate convenience and efficiency. The flat backyard offers endless possibilities to create your own personal paradise. With over 20 acres of land at your disposal, the potential is limitless. Located a short drive to crab houses, restaurants, shopping, Swan Point Golf Club, King George, and La Plata. This one will go quickly, don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property yours!
